To create a translation, run the following command in the ../../lib directory:

wish8.5 lang.tcl <language ISO3066 abbreviation>

Click the "Add Translations" button and when all translations have been
updated, click the "Update" button to save the file and exit the translation
tool.


The following languages have been translated:
---------------------------------------------

Danish                - da.msg
German                - de.msg
Spanish               - es.msg
French                - fr.msg
Hebrew                - he.msg
Italian               - it.msg
Japanese              - ja.msg
Dutch                 - nl.msg
Norwegian             - no.msg
Russian               - ru.msg
Swedish               - sv.msg
Chinese (Traditional) - zh.msg
